---
import Page from '../../layouts/Page.astro';
import SectionBanner from '../../components/ui/SectionBanner.astro';
---

<Page
  title="Workflow Optimization"
  description="Visualization pipeline audits, batch automation, MAXScript utilities, AI-assisted QC. Vision Graphics Kft. — Budapest."
>

  <SectionBanner
    image="/_img/banners/banner-workflow.jpg"
    label="Your Pipeline Can Be Faster"
    title="Workflow Optimization"
    size="page"
    headingLevel="h1"
  />
  <div class="service-page">

    <div class="service-breadcrumb">
      <a href="/services/">Services</a>
      <span>→</span>
      <span>Workflow Optimization</span>
    </div>

    <p class="section-label">Service</p>
    <h2 class="display-lg service-h1">Workflow Optimization</h2>
    <p class="service-tagline-large">Your pipeline is probably slower than it needs to be.</p>

    <div class="service-body-grid">
      <div class="service-main">

        <p class="service-lead">
          Time is money. And you're probably wasting both without realizing it. Most businesses
          think they need more people or better tools. But usually, they just need their current
          tools and people to work better together. We help you spot and fix the daily
          time-wasters that add up.
        </p>

        <h2 class="service-section-h2">What's really slowing you down?</h2>
        <ul class="results-list">
          <li>Where do tasks get stuck?</li>
          <li>Which steps take too long?</li>
          <li>What frustrates your team?</li>
          <li>Where do mistakes keep happening?</li>
        </ul>

      </div>

      <aside class="service-sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-block">
          <h3 class="sidebar-label">Starting point</h3>
          <p class="sidebar-price">from €1,500</p>
          <p class="sidebar-note">Pipeline audit + written report. Implementation quoted separately.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-cta">
          <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary sidebar-btn">Book an Audit</a>
          <a href="/services/3ds-max-tools/" class="btn btn-ghost">3ds Max scripting</a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>

  </div>

  <SectionBanner
    image="/_img/banners/banner-general.jpg"
    label="Quick Wins"
    title="Start Saving Time Today"
    headingLevel="h2"
  />
  <div class="service-section container">
    <p class="section-body">
      We don't do fancy presentations about what might work. We fix what's actually broken.
      No buzzwords. No AI just because it's trendy. We focus on practical fixes that save
      time every day.
    </p>
    <ul class="results-list">
      <li>Connect tools that should talk to each other</li>
      <li>Cut out duplicate work and unnecessary steps</li>
      <li>Fix broken processes that everyone has learned to work around</li>
      <li>Speed up file handling and delivery packaging</li>
      <li>Automate repetitive tasks that waste hours per week</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <SectionBanner
    image="/_img/banners/banner-tech.jpg"
    label="Long-Term Gains"
    title="Build It Right"
    headingLevel="h2"
  />
  <div class="service-section container">
    <p class="section-body">
      Short-term fixes help, but the real value is building workflows that hold up as you
      grow. We build on tools you already have, making changes your team will actually use.
    </p>
    <ul class="results-list">
      <li>Build workflows that make sense and scale</li>
      <li>Set up systems for file management, versioning, and delivery</li>
      <li>Train your team properly so changes stick</li>
      <li>Document everything clearly so nothing lives only in one person's head</li>
      <li>For studios: review and file handoff protocols that prevent version confusion</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <SectionBanner
    image="/_img/banners/banner-services.jpg"
    label="Our Approach"
    title="Watch. Fix. Make It Stick."
    headingLevel="h2"
  />
  <div class="service-section container">
    <div class="process-grid">
      {[
        {
          step: '01',
          title: 'Watch and Learn',
          desc: 'We start with a 1-hour discovery call, then either a remote audit or a site visit. We see how your team actually works, spot the real bottlenecks, and find what\'s causing frustration.',
        },
        {
          step: '02',
          title: 'Fix What Matters',
          desc: 'Within one week we deliver a written report with specific recommendations and time-saving estimates. We start with the biggest time-wasters and test solutions before rolling them out.',
        },
        {
          step: '03',
          title: 'Make It Stick',
          desc: 'We train your team properly and document everything clearly. You can implement yourself or engage us to build the fixes. Either way, you get results you can measure.',
        },
      ].map(p => (
        <div class="process-card">
          <span class="process-step">{p.step}</span>
          <h3 class="process-title">{p.title}</h3>
          <p class="process-desc">{p.desc}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>

</Page>

<style>
  .service-page {
    max-width: 1060px;
    padding-top: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
  }

  .service-breadcrumb {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-faint); margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .service-breadcrumb a { color: var(--color-text-muted); text-decoration: none; transition: color 200ms; }
  .service-breadcrumb a:hover { color: var(--color-accent); }

  .service-h1 { margin: 0.5rem 0 0.75rem; }
  .service-tagline-large { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--fs-h6); font-style: italic; color: var(--color-accent); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .service-lead { font-size: var(--fs-small); color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 65ch; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; }

  .service-body-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 240px; gap: 4rem; align-items: start; }
  .service-main { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }

  .service-section-h2 { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--fs-xs); font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-text-faint); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }

  /* Sub-sections */
  .service-section { padding-block: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); }

  .section-body { font-size: var(--fs-small); color: var(--color-text-muted); max-width: 65ch; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; }

  .results-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
  .results-list li { font-size: var(--fs-small); color: var(--color-text-muted); padding-left: 1.25rem; position: relative; line-height: 1.5; }
  .results-list li::before { content: '→'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--color-accent); font-size: var(--fs-xs); }

  .process-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: var(--color-border); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .process-card { background: var(--color-surface); padding: 1.5rem; transition: background 200ms; }
  .process-card:hover { background: var(--color-surface-2); }
  .process-step { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: var(--color-accent); display: block; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .process-title { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--fs-small); font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .process-desc { font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }

  /* Sidebar */
  .service-sidebar { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; position: sticky; top: 5rem; }
  .sidebar-block { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
  .sidebar-label { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: var(--fs-xs); font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-text-faint); }
  .sidebar-price { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--fs-h5); font-weight: 300; color: var(--color-text); margin: 0; }
  .sidebar-note { font-size: var(--fs-xs); color: var(--color-text-faint); line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; max-width: none; }
  .sidebar-cta { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }
  .sidebar-btn { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .service-body-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .service-sidebar { position: static; }
    .process-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
